<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 01:16:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>你的衣服可能会变得比你更聪明</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/your-clothes-may-become-smarter-than-you</link><description>您可能已经习惯了人们手腕上的智能手表。但智能服装呢？佐治亚大学的研究人员正在探索人们穿的衣服如何潜在地追踪和保护他们的健康。智能纺织品是能够实时监测人体生命体征和运动的面料。它们灵活且轻便，使它们在移动时佩戴更加舒适。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/your-clothes-may-become-smarter-than-you2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 01:16:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/your-clothes-may-become-smarter-than-you</guid></item><item><title>科学家成功从“月球泥土”中收获鹰嘴豆</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-successfully-harvest-chickpeas-from-moon-dirt</link><description>随着美国计划通过即将到来的阿尔忒弥斯二号任务重返月球，一个问题一直存在：未来的月球探险家将吃什么？根据德克萨斯大学奥斯汀分校的最新研究，答案可能是鹰嘴豆。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-successfully-harvest-chickpeas-from-moon-dirt2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 01:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/scientists-successfully-harvest-chickpeas-from-moon-dirt</guid></item><item><title>30股</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/30-shares</link><description>神经技术先驱&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/30-shares.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/30-shares</guid></item><item><title>玻璃化冷冻保存后成年小鼠海马的功能恢复</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/functional-recovery-of-the-adult-murine-hippocampus-after-cryopreservation-by-vitrification</link><description>由于冰形成的损害，冷冻保存成人大脑具有挑战性，传统的冷冻方法无法维持神经结构和功能。玻璃化冷冻提供了一种很有前景的替代方法，但尚未在大脑中进行过研究。在这里，我们展示了成年小鼠海马在脑切片和整个大脑玻璃化后的近乎生理恢复&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/functional-recovery-of-the-adult-murine-hippocampus-after-cryopreservation-by-vitrification</guid></item><item><title>固定剂量 Tavapadon 治疗早期帕金森病：一项随机临床试验</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fixed-dose-tavapadon-for-early-parkinson-disease-a-randomized-clinical-trial</link><description>TEMPO-1 随机临床试验评估了 tavapadon 对患有早期帕金森病的成人的疗效、安全性和耐受性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fixed-dose-tavapadon-for-early-parkinson-disease-a-randomized-clinical-trial2.png" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:16:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fixed-dose-tavapadon-for-early-parkinson-disease-a-randomized-clinical-trial</guid></item><item><title>人类结核病的免疫病理学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/immunopathology-in-human-tuberculosis</link><description>结核分枝杆菌&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/immunopathology-in-human-tuberculosis.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/immunopathology-in-human-tuberculosis</guid></item><item><title>用于基因组测序分析的新计算生物学</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-computational-biology-for-genome-sequencing-analysis</link><description>为了提高超管道 DNA 确定基因组发生变化的能力，科学家们与美国商务部国家标准与技术研究所领导的瓶中基因组联盟合作。通过整合这个公私学术联盟精心验证的资源，研究人员降低了误报率，而没有降低该工具寻找真正遗传变异的精度。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-computational-biology-for-genome-sequencing-analysis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-computational-biology-for-genome-sequencing-analysis</guid></item><item><title>钱德拉解决了黑洞增长减速的原因</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/chandra-resolves-why-black-holes-hit-the-brakes-on-growth</link><description>天文学家对天体物理学中一个长期存在的谜团有了答案：为什么今天超大质量黑洞的增长比过去低得多？使用美国宇航局钱德拉 X 射线天文台和其他 X 射线望远镜进行的一项研究发现，超大质量黑洞无法像遥远的过去那样快速消耗物质。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/chandra-resolves-why-black-holes-hit-the-brakes-on-growth.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/chandra-resolves-why-black-holes-hit-the-brakes-on-growth</guid></item><item><title>伟哥可降低患阿尔茨海默病的风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/viagra-associated-with-reduced-risk-of-alzheimers-disease</link><description>一项新研究的结果支持进一步研究西地那非作为阿尔茨海默病的可能治疗方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/viagra-associated-with-reduced-risk-of-alzheimers-disease.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:16:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/viagra-associated-with-reduced-risk-of-alzheimers-disease</guid></item><item><title>磁铁将软超材料中的随机吸附转变为可重复的序列</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/magnets-turn-random-snapping-in-soft-metamaterials-into-repeatable-sequences</link><description>将图案切割成弹性材料可以将这些材料展开成新的形状，研究人员现在已经证明了通过磁化材料来控制展开顺序的能力。这项工作代表了我们对超材料行为理解的根本性进步，并且还证明了其在吸收动能的应用中的实用性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/magnets-turn-random-snapping-in-soft-metamaterials-into-repeatable-sequences3.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 23:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/magnets-turn-random-snapping-in-soft-metamaterials-into-repeatable-sequences</guid></item></channel></rss>